peridot is  Console Twitter Client.
This Client is written by Java.

It includes The Apache Software Foundation Libraries.
You can see license term at http://www.apache.org/licenses/

How to use
1.Java -jar peridot.jar(if you use in utf8, you input "java -Dfile.encoding=UTF-8 -jar peridot.jar")
2.Go to URL & Enter Pin Code
3.enjoy it!

4.
commands:
/rep id tweet     :  Reply to id
/fav id           :  Add to favorite
/unfav id         :  Remove from favorite
/rm id            :  Remove post
/rt id            :  ReTweet

/find str         :  search "str"

/rep              :  Show Mention
/fav              :  Show favorites
/get              :  Show TimeLine

/exit             :  exit
